name: entervoCheckoutPluginBraintree
summary: Plugin for implementing entervo checkout flow into 3rd party appspec.
description:
entervoCheckoutPluginBraintree
This is a plugin for 3rd party integrators to include Scheidt & Bachmann entervi (tm) checkout logic into their own applicationspec.
The complete flow and communication with the S&B backend is handled by the plugin and can be used with a few lines of code only.
